# Dastan 0.2.0

 * Native GTK 4 and Libadwaita Markdown viewer
 * GitHub Flavored Markdown rendering via vendored cmark-gfm
 * Native LaTeX math typesetting via vendored Lasem
 * Right-to-left and mixed-direction text support
 * Bundled Shabnam and Latin Modern fonts
 * Flatpak, AppImage, and distribution packaging support